{"hdbb75bccgfe5fg48a9g841cgaf93b5d4e30d": ["... you're both twice as tall as me but have half the bloody backbone!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "0920da0b-0ae2-05cc-1059-2a0de5cc46b6"], "h44bd974eg7e01g478ag8261g896732fcec2d": ["But we don't know what that <i>thing </i>even is! And what about the crypt?", "b5c913f9-f081-45bd-8e95-e34d0735b645", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "81323220-a52f-1032-2f37-4f935e72ea1a"], "h058eae79g6aa2g491bg8e64gb102c00454ee": ["I'm telling you - it's a ship.", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "bb514728-0382-076c-3c4d-cf5e7ac29247"], "h53c3ceceg2cafg4aa6g98a8g39ec5b91a732": ["And the crypt can wait! Mari and Barton have been trying to break in for days. Now we - <i>stop!</i>", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "2a6b410e-8f3e-3958-eb12-959d3a197fb6"], "h1cbb2a5fg6c7eg45a4gbb0dg73e8cc2d55c9": ["Got ourselves competition already! I dunno what the hells you are, but that's our ship!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "ea738c8a-c88b-c322-ad81-0ce4b1e504e9"], "h1e6e802fgf352g49c6g95bege76a41859a1a": ["Got ourselves competition already! That's our ship!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "ea738c8a-c88b-c322-ad81-0ce4b1e504e9"], "h57adc6fbg90c0g4b00g8dc6ge4c3ed636ba9": ["I mean no harm - I'm just looking around.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "1eadea55-392e-f21f-1122-f23ddcb3f202"], "h67cc6d57g251ag40efgab63gd0ba81527f4a": ["First you look, then you touch, then you take!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "73b3d154-4b61-d980-2e35-72237b577013"], "hf79b4b28g8f43g498aga8e2gfb878f7f6170": ["The only thing we're sharing with you is our pointy ends - get 'im!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "95b7e274-d7b0-e250-c933-f191cb3b5b72"], "h61835925gce5dg4a5bg895fg5a5caa04ad33": ["The only thing we're sharing with you is our pointy ends - get 'er!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "95b7e274-d7b0-e250-c933-f191cb3b5b72"], "ha6565613gce19g459ag9243gcfc398d41772": ["That ship is full of monsters. I wouldn't go near it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "5dcdfbc5-7c8a-19b9-2bef-04b70bb5f632"], "he054800ag96b4g4436gb4d8gdd0ad1c1a534": ["Well, uh, in that case...", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "c4bfc70b-4eac-398d-5044-17627b415a28"], "h6a35ad05g4872g4176g9a4agfeca89230aa7": ["C'mon you lot, no point in gettin' killed. Second worm gets the cheese, an' all...", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "69bbf2c4-e5b0-f276-6867-326b5075a5c8"], "h73e77ed5g447cg481bgaf05gc7546ab2192e": ["Uh, second <i>mouse </i>gets the cheese, no?", "b5c913f9-f081-45bd-8e95-e34d0735b645", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "ce616418-8df3-f3ad-f255-20ad1860e2be"], "he885a596ge980g4a77g9ab6g7a8c288e812e": ["Nobody's getting any damn cheese! Now move it!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "d0542c18-d9da-6ce5-2a83-5ff434cc6d21"], "hf4bea2aeg3ff9g4a6dgba46g144ef99aa917": ["You're all hot air - think you can get us to leave that bounty to you? Not a chance!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "a800c0bf-29e1-3e9f-5ff6-581b7dcf0f2f"], "hf23f1752gb942g473egb2d4gf9375f2f22ed": ["What're you lot waiting for? <i>Get 'im!</i>", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "de5b6976-9695-a66c-fd4c-4194d10c14e2"], "hba15f002gf6a5g40f4g915ag422cbb4509f7": ["What're you lot waiting for? <i>Get 'er!</i>", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "de5b6976-9695-a66c-fd4c-4194d10c14e2"], "h89f0988ag3592g4d46gbd54g538868e8b10d": ["I think that ship's an invasion force. Run while you can!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "12634287-93ab-24a2-85bf-c16aa0db7609"], "h55c56a87g7e18g46d9g8aabgdc1e6c42afa0": ["The only thing you own is your life. Leave before I take that too.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "1225ed89-7b32-c9c0-34b5-a8cd39e4c199"], "h39d18368g7d2eg49b4ga457gb185dc674054": ["<i>Just grin, baring your fangs.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "f9392f9d-46e3-3b47-30f8-dee0edfc52fb"], "h549d9f21g90f4g4891gb985g6a2d32d077b2": ["That is my kin's prize, not yours.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "8259d8d3-b028-ebde-487a-00e8dfc77d27"], "h8be470cfg7011g4076g946dg60cd9e572178": ["Oh yeah? Well, I don't see any of your kin here to claim it!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "7a3b0d49-750d-cd3f-0de2-b3f6e7455412"], "h72955042gb763g4b6dgaa87g238fcb959654": ["What's wrong with his face? Freak.", "b5c913f9-f081-45bd-8e95-e34d0735b645", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "6ed7eee2-f485-483e-3b84-1a5c5e121b60"], "h4b14ed9dgf6b9g4a54ga860gd0ed01ff3db2": ["What's wrong with her face? Freak.", "b5c913f9-f081-45bd-8e95-e34d0735b645", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "6ed7eee2-f485-483e-3b84-1a5c5e121b60"], "h5ff7516bg1da2g4d3bgaa62g65fcf732a16c": ["<i>Dead</i> freak. Get 'im!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "6fe2d59b-a249-ae82-54a0-28b857ebfd79"], "h28e337dcg65b7g4a08g8b63g6d44b9b76370": ["<i>Dead</i> freak. Get 'er!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "6fe2d59b-a249-ae82-54a0-28b857ebfd79"], "h717494c0g28f2g423cg98d1g4ad8c75d7118": ["Nothing's yours but your life - and I can take that from you just as easily.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "12ffcb1c-18ad-99a5-3148-7c35de7f4bdc"], "h0b2f3770g23c5g4fd1g9c34g6f172b2bf91c": ["Oh yeah? Well we're... we're -", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "72168b73-8b37-2443-be66-151501e07519"], "hfb00b3c1g93c1g45eagb62cg6fa6a3b58a12": ["I ain't fighting him. Not a chance.", "b5c913f9-f081-45bd-8e95-e34d0735b645", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "b92de5dc-8b8a-d6cd-e677-4605a8c61d0b"], "h433a75a0g0c20g40feg8dc8g86cbbc6de5e5": ["I ain't fighting her. Not a chance.", "b5c913f9-f081-45bd-8e95-e34d0735b645", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "b92de5dc-8b8a-d6cd-e677-4605a8c61d0b"], "hb86b72f8g61fag41e9g9ea2g26eecc609088": ["... we're, uh... we're leaving! C'mon, move it!", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "beac49ad-1e9b-0c08-7806-3f99da225a8f"], "hd63438b3g8b9fg4101gb242g59554910c049": ["Take your best shot - you'll only get one.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "66dd737d-9291-b021-2b1b-5d457b248ad4"], "h7c636ccegd96cg4ed4ga8d4g537e8b92310f": ["That ship's full of poisonous vapours. Probably demonic. I'd stay away.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "034090e2-d6e7-9173-e893-5a7dd19f2b1f"], "hbcf63513g9c9ag4cbega22fg6fe86cf33eef": ["Poisonous wha...?", "538e38b9-e3a4-452a-8369-60eb1fe8c40d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "5c2dd205-f535-27bf-55ad-b4ea2d5a86d3"], "he045beb3g2726g43ffg83b5g9031150c7cc7": ["See? That thing could be carrying a plague for all we know!", "b5c913f9-f081-45bd-8e95-e34d0735b645", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "914318fb-55af-572e-b8dd-2a2b355f801e"], "ha9426b14gc106g430cg9627g33219a395da6": ["<i>Attack.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Chapel\\CHA_Outside_BanditInteraction.html", "348f2d00-fe6f-94e7-c0fb-3e96961e4d6b"]}